# README Documentation Index

When adding, renaming, moving, or deleting documentation files, update `README.md` in the same change.

Keep the README aligned with the current document structure:

- Update the document organization table when a new major folder or documentation area is added.
- Add newly planned or created documents to the appropriate roadmap or document list.
- Remove or rename README references when document files are removed or renamed.
- Do not list implementation-only assets as primary documentation entries.
